item.description:
At this month's meeting we will have a presentation by one of our own members ... Sidney Pratt.

Sid is going to show us some of the amazing things he is able to do with his cameras. He plans to start with an overview of Adobe's Camera Raw using a couple of good examples. When he's done with that he plans to show us how to take a 3-D photo. If time allows he'd like to wrap up with a little "quiz".

We will be meeting in the Mara Auditorium inside of Webster Hall. When you enter the building, the entrance to the Mara Auditorium is straight ahead. We will have signs posted within the building.

Hope to see you all there!!
item.name: October Manchester Adobe User Group Meeting
